Available topics in the introverse

Source: vignettes/available_topics.Rmd
available_topics.Rmd

As of July 19, 2021, the following topics (organized by category) are available in the introverse. To get help for any topic, run get_help("topic").

Operators and Magrittr pipe

show_topics("operators")
#> 
#>  "assignment"
#>  "logical"
#>  "mathematical"
show_topics("magrittr")
#> 
#>  "%<>%"
#>  "%>%"


Base R

This category includes all functions that come with R, not only those in the “base” R package.

show_topics("base")
#> 
#>  "as.character"
#>  "as.factor"
#>  "as.numeric"
#>  "c"
#>  "ceiling"
